      "span_text": "BRAT is based on our previously released opensource STAV text annotation visualiser [CITATION_1] , which was designed to help users gain an understanding of complex annotations involving a large number of different semantic types, dense, partially overlapping text annotations, and non-projective sets of connections between annotations."
